high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn around to the counter behind you.
Place the fork in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in the sink.

high_descs: Go into the kitchen, face the sink.
Pick the fork up out of the sink.
Turn around  to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the fork into the green bin behind the statue.
Pick up the green bin with the fork in it.
Turn around and move to the sink.
Place the green bin and fork in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a fork into a green bin, place that combination into the sink.

high_descs: Walk straight and then make a turn to the right
Walk over to the sink
Grab the fork from the sink
Carry it over to the counter
Place the fork inside the green cup
Go back to the kitchen sink
Place the green cup and the fork in the sink
anns.task_desc: Gathering the dirty dishes and putting them in the sink

high_descs: Turn right, head to the fridge, turn right, head for the sink, and turn right.
Pick up the fork.
Turn around and face the trophy.
Put the fork in the glass.
Pick up the glass.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a glass, and put the glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn around and face the counter with a statue on it.
Place the fork in the green cup behind the statue.
Pick up the green cup from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the green cup in the front left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a green cup with a fork in it into the sink.
